# Repos under ~/crown, ~/personal, ~/confelicity that bmad-update-all should
# ignore even if they contain a _bmad/ directory.
#
# Format: one path per line, relative to $HOME.
# Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.

# Crown's canonical knowledge repo. BMAD scaffolding doesn't belong here -
# it's noise for the Crown team's Claude Team Project that indexes this repo
# via the GitHub connector. _bmad/, _bmad-output/, .claude/skills/bmad-*/
# are gitignored in the repo itself; this entry stops `quick-update` from
# re-creating them on disk.
crown/crown-knowledge
